Created this app using vite 
npm create vite@latest

Dependencies downloaded:

npm install @reduxjs/toolkit react-redux
npm insall react-router-dom
npm insall appwrite
npm install @tinymce/tinymce-react
npm install html-react-parser
npm install react-hook-form


We use appwrite for the backend part.
We use tinymce for visual code editor.
We use html-react-parser because we will save the data in html tags form so we need to parse them.
We use react-hook-form for creating auth form.

